<div class="container-fluid text-primary d-flex justify-content-center py-3 ">
    <main>
        <h1>Safety and Security</h1>
        <section id="meeting-safety">
            <h2>Meeting Safety</h2>
            <p><strong>Plan Your Meeting Publicly:</strong> Always meet in a well-populated area with plenty of people around.</p>
            <p><strong>Inform Someone:</strong> Let a friend or family member know your plans, including where you're going, who you're meeting, and when you expect to return.</p>
            <p><strong>Use Your Own Transport:</strong> Arrange your own transportation to and from the meeting location. Avoid accepting rides from people you don't know well.</p>
            <p><strong>Trust Your Instincts:</strong> If something feels off or uncomfortable, trust your instincts and leave the situation.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="online-interaction">
            <h2>Online Interaction Safety</h2>
            <p><strong>Protect Your Personal Information:</strong> Avoid sharing sensitive information such as your home address, phone number, or financial details with strangers.</p>
            <p><strong>Be Cautious with Personal Details:</strong> Share only necessary information and avoid oversharing personal details until you’re comfortable.</p>
            <p><strong>Verify Profiles:</strong> If you’re uncertain about someone, try to verify their profile information through additional means, such as mutual connections.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="reporting-blocking">
            <h2>Reporting and Blocking</h2>
            <p><strong>Report Suspicious Behavior:</strong> Report any suspicious or inappropriate behavior through the app. Ensure reports are reviewed promptly and appropriate actions are taken.</p>
            <p><strong>Block Unwanted Contacts:</strong> Use the block feature to remove users who make you feel uncomfortable or behave inappropriately.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="emergency-contacts">
            <h2>Emergency Contacts</h2>
            <p><strong>Emergency Help:</strong> Contact local emergency services if needed. Have emergency contact numbers readily available.</p>
            <p><strong>App Support:</strong> Reach out to our support team if you need assistance or encounter any issues.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="safety-tips">
            <h2>Safety Tips for Specific Situations</h2>
            <p><strong>First Meetings:</strong> Always meet in public places during daylight hours. Choose locations that are familiar and well-lit.</p>
            <p><strong>Group Meetings:</strong> If meeting a group of people, ensure you’re aware of the group dynamics and have mutual connections if possible.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="encouraging-safe-practices">
            <h2>Encouraging Safe Practices</h2>
            <p><strong>Be Honest and Respectful:</strong> Communicate respectfully and honestly with others to build a trustworthy environment.</p>
            <p><strong>Follow Community Guidelines:</strong> Adhere to the app’s community guidelines to foster a safe and respectful community.</p>
        </section>
    </main>
</div>

